{"tid":341763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（軍事機密）川普怒了！美軍高官爆：明年將與北韓「開戰」","createTime":"2017-07-31T05:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T09:22:55.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c22db21828f7e3c0798ee5fd64822dad73fa2ac9","tid":341763,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T05:15:34.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕北韓頻頻進行飛彈試射，美國忍無可忍了？一名美國高級軍官透露，五角大廈已擬定一項計畫，川普可能在明年下令對北韓進行軍事攻擊，摧毀北韓的核武設施。<br />\n這名官員接受《每日郵報》專訪指出，美國欲透過軍事行動，一舉摧毀北韓位在深山的核子武器設施，這個打擊北韓獨裁者金正恩的做法，將是「美國向北韓開戰的重要一步」。<br />\n五角大廈指出，北韓日前發設的洲際彈到導彈飛行距離約1000公里，最後落入日本海域。美國專家表示，若此飛彈用更平的彈道發射，可能可打到美國中部的芝加哥甚至東部的紐約。<br />\n報導指出，美軍昨天在南韓進行實彈演習，川普則誓言要採取一切必要措施來確保美國及其盟國的安全。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2148206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2148206&d=ioBbEwQ8bECJkkkZqHTizROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=9706e4d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2148206&h=f906241f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2148206</a><br />\n北韓有核武，美國中一個都唔得掂"},{"pid":"11af8f9ea04ae2db0fe89347c316baa3fb44bd34","tid":341763,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T05:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055c3edf52efd2233507cf1b3eda2f68d4689ffa","tid":341763,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c8867a295a8ebb0c42089fe1c91be243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc8867a295a8ebb0c42089fe1c91be243.jpg&h=42c8b918&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3be48a5f8b12aef7ab777c6d7a5f21475adbe160","tid":341763,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"機密暴光, 唔洗打lu"},{"pid":"9028e04f2e2a7154d06acc8